--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7e99d2aa6db43f2478d3198a0ca05313, type: 3}
  m_Name: Level 5
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueInfo:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Oh? Look who is back.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: The Mr. Professional Food Critic himself.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 1
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Haha. Very funny.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "So? What\u2019ll it be today?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "I heard your B\xE1nh Cu\u1ED1n started getting attention online."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Well, maybe your reviews helped a little.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Then let\u2019s see if it lives up to the hype"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 26b8df2c53d25774a98417f35663a454, type: 2}
    charText: "Isn\u2019t that the food critic everyone\u2019s talking about online
      lately?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6cbc2fe164d1be146948a6741ae3067e, type: 2}
    charText: "Oh no\u2026 We need to inform the chef!"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: Good evening.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: I heard that a famous food critic has come to visit us today.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Hm? Famous might be a bit too much.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: "But yes. I\u2019m here for your Ph\u1EDF."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: Then I shall personally prepare it for you.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Looking forward to it.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: How was the dish?
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: The broth was incredibly rich
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: "The savoury flavor wasn\u2019t overwhelming, yet it lingered naturally"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "And the beef\u2026"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: So tender that it almost melted the moment it touched my tongue.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: "Hahaha! I\u2019m relieved to hear that."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "Though\u2026"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: Hm?
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: The noodles were slightly softer than I expected.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: A few extra seconds less in the water would have improved the texture
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: "\u2026I see."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: But overall?
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: It deserves the popularity it has
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66353d41dda40ed4b916194c7b110f3c, type: 2}
    charText: Thank you for your honest review.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "Giving criticism like this feels\u2026 surprisingly good."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
